{"word":"G4555 - σάρδινος - sárdinos - sar'-dee-nos - Sardine","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σάρδινος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sárdinos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sar'-dee-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sardine</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பதுமராகம் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"carnelian"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G4556 - σάρδιος - sárdios - sar'-dee-os/4556\">G4556</a>; <i>sardine</i> (<a href=\"#/G3037 - λίθος - líthos - lee'-thos/3037\">G3037</a> being implied), that is, a gem, so called: - sardine.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}